topic :

secret & config map

why we need configmap and secret what is the purpose in k8s

using config map and secret we can pass the env variable to our application 

config map :  not encrypted value >> voluemount is possible  : using volume mount we can pass the env to the application without restart

secret : encrypted value

command:

how to create a config map

kubectl apply -f configmap.yml

how to create a secret 

kubectl apply -f secret.yml

how to view config map 

kubectl get cm

how to view secret 

kubectl get secret